<p style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#0F2D57;margin:10px 0 12px 0;">Regional infrastructure push — G42 / du partnerships (UAE)</p>

<!-- Row 3: Summary (no image available) -->
<p style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#333333;line-height:1.5;margin:0 0 14px 0;">G42 and du announced partnerships with Microsoft to accelerate Abu Dhabi government digital strategy and regional cloud/infrastructure initiatives. The collaboration is poised to expand local cloud capacity and AI deployment in the UAE, with implications for public-sector digitalisation, procurement and local partner opportunities.</p>

