<p style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#1A1A1A;line-height:1.5;margin:0;">Microsoft welcomes collaboration with G42 and du to expand local cloud capacity and accelerate AI adoption in Abu Dhabi; leaders should frame this as aligned with Microsoft UAE's mission and the UAE National AI Strategy to support compliant, locally delivered cloud and partner-led digital transformation.</p>
