<p style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#1A1A1A;line-height:1.5;margin:4px 0 0 0;">This partnership directly accelerates Abu Dhabi's and broader UAE public-sector and partner-led cloud initiatives by expanding regionally hosted capacity and enabling compliant AI deployments aligned to the National AI Strategy. It is immediately actionable for Microsoft UAE sellers, opening opportunities in public-sector procurements, local managed services, and partner-led solutioning.</p>
