<p style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#0F2D57;margin:10px 0 12px 0;">Azure OpenAI — enterprise foundational models (MAI)</p>

<!-- Row 3: Summary -->
<p style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#333333;line-height:1.5;margin:0 0 14px 0;">Microsoft released a suite of MAI foundational models (MAI-Transcribe, MAI-Voice, MAI-Image) as part of Azure OpenAI updates. This expands enterprise access to multimodal capabilities on Azure, enabling organizations to integrate speech, voice and image understanding into their applications and workflows.</p>

